.aider.chat.history.md
.aider.input.history
.aider.tags.cache.v4/
.aider.memory.md

# --- Demo videos: hosted as GitHub attachments, never committed ---
# Raw captures exceed GitHub's 100 MB per-file limit; only the small
# highlight GIFs in docs/images/ live in git.
*.mov
*.mp4
